etomica.graph.traversal

Interface Traversal

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTraversal, BiconectedNodalPoint, Biconnected, BreadthFirst, DepthFirst

    public interface Traversal
    This interface generalizes algorithms that traverse the nodes of a graph. The traversal allows a visitor to visit each of the nodes as they are traversed. If the graph is not connected, only one connected component is traversed.
